##Language-Level Data
#This directory contains the language-level datasets used in the study. These files include both the multilingual LLM responses collected through API queries and the processed language-level datasets used to construct country-level estimates and subsequent analyses.

##input_language.xlsx:
#This file contains the language-level moral judgment dataset used in the analyses. For each language, it reports the average LLM response to each WVS/EVS survey item after aggregating repeated model queries.

##response_chatgpt_WVS.xlsx:
#This file contains the raw multilingual LLM responses collected for the World Values Survey (WVS) items. For each language and survey item, it reports the prompts submitted to the model, the individual responses obtained across repeated API calls, and the corresponding average response.

##response_chatgpt_EVS.xlsx:
#This file contains the raw multilingual LLM responses collected for the European Values Study (EVS) items. It reports the language-specific responses generated by the model and the corresponding average values used to construct the language-level dataset.
